{"tid":1158492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女監爆性侵案 壯女囂張嗆「紅燈擋不住流氓」","createTime":"2019-05-17T04:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T04:45:17.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"12bdfc1fab545e2b31516f33565e84d6e67e9f3a","tid":1158492,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T04:08:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">台中</span>女子監獄爆發暴力性侵案！一名重達百公斤的壯碩女受刑人，連續兩天壓制舍友小玲（化名），讓她無法掙脫並以手指性侵，還囂張嗆：「紅燈擋不住流氓」，高等法院昨依強制性交罪判壯碩女4年2月徒刑。<br />\n <br />\n判決指出，2016年12月29日晚間，小玲在戒護窗前等候獄方人員發藥時，一名有傷害前科的壯碩女舍友，突然從後方環抱小玲將她壓制倒地。<br />\n <br />\n壯碩女親吻小玲頸部、胸部等處予以強制猥褻。小玲叫喊「不要」，壯碩女警告小玲說「如果妳現在不要，晚一點睡覺時妳會更慘」，並恐嚇說，她在監所的女友曾因反抗，遭她打得很慘，讓小玲非常害怕，壯碩女非常得意，還自比流氓，嗆說「「紅燈擋不住流氓」等話，小玲連兩天遭壯碩女性侵。<br />\n <br />\n事後小玲一再自殘，半夜作惡夢，還被診斷出有「泛焦慮症」，最後鼓起勇氣提告。"},{"pid":"85403a04f22e319fe240b0feaa33429b08301fe2","tid":1158492,"uid":159444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T04:11:38.000Z","msg":"新情節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef31c47189c2e88cd4c833634fe50493ae57423","tid":1158492,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T04:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/ekr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2Fekr.gif&h=56167da4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b981a483ee8d94da089b5a8818fdb89f81a96db0","tid":1158492,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T04:39:37.000Z","msg":"一百公斤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af455525c2eb90ec8de54cbb915b4df495e32b50","tid":1158492,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cef31c47189c2e88cd4c833634fe50493ae57423","tid":1158492,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T04:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img sr